Standard Life plc provides an array of financial services and products, including insurance, investments, savings, mortgages, pension plans and healthcare.

On March 4, 2017, Standard Life and Aberdeen Asset Management are in discussing merger between the two companies. Under the terms,… MoreStandard Life plc provides an array of financial services and products, including insurance, investments, savings, mortgages, pension plans and healthcare.

On March 4, 2017, Standard Life and Aberdeen Asset Management are in discussing merger between the two companies. Under the terms, Aberdeen shareholders would own 33.3 per cent and Standard Life shareholders would own 66.7 per cent of the combined group.






